---
import SectionTitle from "./SectionTitle.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="py-16">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <SectionTitle
      title="Mon Approche"
      subtitle="Comment je conçois des solutions web performantes"
    />

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-12">
      <!-- Architecture -->
      <div class="text-center space-y-4">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-text-main">Architecture Propre</h3>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Je privilégie le code SOLID, les design patterns et une structure claire pour faciliter la maintenance et l'évolution.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Performance -->
      <div class="text-center space-y-4">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-text-main">Performance Optimisée</h3>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Cache intelligent, requêtes optimisées, lazy loading... Chaque projet est conçu pour être rapide et scalable.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Collaboration -->
      <div class="text-center space-y-4">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-text-main">Collaboration Agile</h3>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Communication transparente, livraisons régulières et adaptation continue pour répondre aux besoins métiers.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mt-16 p-8 bg-card rounded-xl border border-border">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent mb-1">6+</div>
        <div class="text-muted text-xs">Ans d'expérience</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent mb-1">50+</div>
        <div class="text-muted text-xs">Projets livrés</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent mb-1">15+</div>
        <div class="text-muted text-xs">Technologies</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent mb-1">100%</div>
        <div class="text-muted text-xs">Satisfaction client</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>